      "es": "",
      "en": "Return a string containing linesep characters as required to correctly fold the header according to policy. A cte_type of 8bit will be treated as if it were 7bit, since headers may not contain arbitrary binary data. If utf8 is False, non-ASCII data will be RFC 2047 encoded."
